data.description: Great Brick home in Belvedere Park - Great School Location. Home was \renovated in 2011. Updated kitchen with granite countertops, 36 inch cabinets, can lights and tiled floors. SS refrigerator to stay. The kitchen features Desk nook & pantry. Separate laundry closet. Master is a good size with rare walk in closet, black slate in shower, double shower head, and double vanity with plenty of storage. Hardwoods throughout. 4-sided brick, carport\nice level fenced yard. New roof & gutters less than 10yrs. old. Across the street from Wadsworth school.
